This is how to words_in_sentence of sentence:
  When isarray of sentence is yes, then:
    Remember that text is ""
    Remember that i is 0
    Do this sentence's length times:
      Remember that text is "{text}{tostring of item i in sentence}"
      Increase i by 1
    End do
  But, if not:
    Remember that text is sentence
  End when
  Remember that words is []
  Remember that current is ""
  Remember that i is 0
  Do this text's length times:
    Remember that ch is item i in text
    When ch is " ", then:
      When current is not "", then:
        Add words to current
        Remember that current is ""
      End when
    But, if not:
      Remember that current is "{current}{ch}"
    End when
    Increase i by 1
  End do
  When current is not "", then:
    Add words to current
  End when
  When words' length is 4, then:
    The answer is item 1 in words
  But, if not:
    When words' length is 3, then:
      The answer is "{item 1 in words} {item 2 in words}"
    End when
  End when
